<h1>pc 5 marzo - Lotte operaie negli USA - info</h1>
<p>Author: maoist</p>
<p>Description: Inchiesta apparsa sul “ The Guardian ”                 sulle sfide che sta affrontando il nuovo processo di                 sinda...</p>
<p>Time: 2023-03-05T07:44:00+01:00</p>
<p>Images: ['<a href="https://contropiano.org/img/2023/03/Amazon-Usa-workers-720x300.webp">Amazon-Usa-workers-720x300.webp</a>', '<a href="https://contropiano.org/img/2023/03/Amazon-teamsters.webp">Amazon-teamsters.webp</a>', '<a href="https://contropiano.org/img/2023/03/Stati-Uniti-lavoratrici.webp">Stati-Uniti-lavoratrici.webp</a>', '<a href="https://assets.contropiano.org/img/2023/03/Stati-Uniti-workers.jpg">Stati-Uniti-workers.jpg</a>']</p>
